headline: Republic Services (NYSE:RSG) Misses Q4 CY2025 Sales Expectations
summary: Waste management company Republic Services (NYSE:RSG) fell short of the market’s revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025 as sales rose 2.2% year on year to $4.14 billion. The company’s full-year revenue guidance of $17.1 billion at the midpoint came in 1.3% below analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.76 per share was 7.9% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: Republic Services, Inc. Reports Fourth Quarter and Full-Year 2025 Results; Provides 2026 Full-Year Financial Guidance
summary: Republic Services, Inc. (NYSE: RSG) today reported net income of $545 million, or $1.76 per diluted share, for the three months ended December 31, 2025, versus $512 million, or $1.63 per diluted share, for 2024. Excluding certain expenses and other items, on an adjusted basis, net income for the three months ended December 31, 2025, was $547 million, or $1.76 per diluted share, versus $497 million, or $1.58 per diluted share, for the comparable 2024 period.
